This software is distributed under a Dual-State Honor System.

OPERATIONAL DIRECTIVE:
This codebase is designed for raw system latency optimization. Your right to
use, modify, and distribute this software is dictated entirely by your
self-assessed financial status and your personal integrity.

STATE 0 (Restricted Capital):
If you are financially restricted or cannot afford disposable software, you
are granted a permanent, irrevocable license to use this software free of
charge. Take it, optimize your system, and use that performance to find your
breathing space.

STATE 1 (Disposable Capital):
If you possess premium hardware or consider yourself to have disposable
income, you are requested by this license to fund the development.

Payment Node: [Status: PENDING CONFIGURATION]

Directive: Until the routing node is active, the software remains free of
charge for all. However, by using this software in a state of financial
surplus, you acknowledge a future obligation to the developer. This is a
social contract binded to you as a user; when the node goes live, you are
expected to fulfill the balance for the value already received.

NO ENFORCEMENT:
There is no DRM. There is no telemetry. There is no hardware execution lock.
This license is enforced entirely by your own integrity. If you have the
capital and choose not to pay, the software will still execute flawlessly,
but the social contract remains unfulfilled.

